game: Age of Empires II: Difinitive Edition

steps.description: Queue up 4 vils and build 2 houses with starting vils. Send all vils to sheep
Send your sixth vil to build a lumber camp. Send the next 3 vils to chop wood.
Send your tenth and eleventh vils to lure/collect boars.
Build 2 houses with your twelfth vil, then send it to berries.
With your thirteenth vil, build a mill on the berries. Send the next 2 vils to berries
Send your sixteenth, seventeenth, and eighteenth vils to collect food from boars and sheep under your TC
Send your nineteenth and twentieth vils to wood. Queue up Loom and then click up to Feudal Age
